  "slug": "open-together",
  "title": "Open Together",
  "description": "Open matching double doors, trapdoors, and fence gates with a single click.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Open Together</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> makes matching doors, trapdoors, and fence gates open as a group when placed next to each other. Open one block, and connected neighbours follow automatically, making double doors and wider entrances feel natural to use. 🚪</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The mod removes repetitive clicks during everyday gameplay while preserving vanilla behaviour and building styles. It works with manual interactions and can also support vanilla mechanics such as redstone when installed on the server. ⚡</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Unlike most similar solutions, the mod can be installed on the client, the server, or both. Server installation provides the most complete and consistent experience for all players. Client-only use also works on multiplayer servers without the mod, but only for your own manual interactions and not for server-side effects like redstone. 🌐</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🚪 Double Doors:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Open matching neighbouring doors together for smoother entrances and cleaner builds.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🪤 Double Trapdoors:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Linked trapdoors open together, making floor hatches and decorative builds easier to use.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🚧 Double Fence Gates:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Adjacent fence gates can open as one, perfect for wider paths, farms, and animal pens.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚡ Redstone Support:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> When installed server-side, supported blocks can open together through vanilla-style interactions, including redstone.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌐 Flexible Installation:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Works on client, server, or both, with server installation providing the most complete multiplayer experience.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">👤 Client-Only Multiplayer Use:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Can still help on servers without the mod installed by opening nearby matching blocks.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🛠️ Configurable Behaviour:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Enable or disable grouped opening for each supported block type and adjust behaviour to suit your preferences.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🏷️ Modded Block Support:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Compatible modded doors, trapdoors, and fence gates can be included through block tags.</span></li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⌨️ Quick Toggle:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Includes an optional keybind to temporarily enable or disable grouped opening.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION OPTIONAL ON CLIENT &amp; OPTIONAL ON SERVER</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/natural-waters\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/naturalwaters/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/easy-anvils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/hovering-hotbar\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/hoveringhotbar/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/opentogether/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
